      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9323-102"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> 是以下异常的基类：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-102"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> is the base class for the following exceptions:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9323-103"><xref:System.DivideByZeroException>，在除数为0时整数相除引发。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-103"><xref:System.DivideByZeroException>, which is thrown in integer division when the divisor is 0.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="f9323-104">例如，尝试将10除以0会引发 <xref:System.DivideByZeroException> 异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-104">For example, attempting to divide 10 by 0 throws a <xref:System.DivideByZeroException> exception.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9323-105"><xref:System.NotFiniteNumberException>，当对或返回、、、、、以及 <xref:System.Double.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Double.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Double.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Single.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Single.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Single.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType> 使用的编程语言不支持这些值时，将引发此异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-105"><xref:System.NotFiniteNumberException>, which is thrown when an operation is performed on or returns <xref:System.Double.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Double.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Double.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, and the programming language used does not support those values.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9323-106"><xref:System.OverflowException>，在操作的结果超出目标数据类型的边界时引发。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-106"><xref:System.OverflowException>, which is thrown when the result of an operation is outside the bounds of the target data type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9323-107">也就是说，它小于数字的 `MinValue` 属性或大于其 `MaxValue` 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-107">That is, it is less than a number's `MinValue` property or greater than its `MaxValue` property.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="f9323-108">例如，如果尝试将 200 + 200 赋给一个值，则会 <xref:System.Byte> 引发 <xref:System.OverflowException> 异常，因为400大于256，即 <xref:System.Byte> 数据类型的上限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-108">For example, attempting to assign 200 + 200 to a <xref:System.Byte> value throws an <xref:System.OverflowException> exception, since 400 greater than 256, the upper bound of the <xref:System.Byte> data type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9323-109">你的代码不应处理或引发此异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-109">Your code should not handle or throw this exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9323-110">相反，应处理或引发其派生类之一，因为它更精确地指示错误的确切性质。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-110">Instead, you should either handle or throw one of its derived classes, since it more precisely indicates the exact nature of the error.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9323-111">有关实例的初始属性值的列表<xref:System.ArithmeticException>，请参阅<xref:System.ArithmeticException>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-111">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.ArithmeticException>, see the <xref:System.ArithmeticException> constructors.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9323-112"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> 使用 HRESULT COR_E_ARITHMETIC，其值为0x80070216。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9323-112"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_ARITHMETIC, which has the value 0x80070216.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
